// import { Routes, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import '../../App.css'
import { Section } from '../../Components/SectionSimple/SectionSimple.jsx'
import { TextBlock } from '../../Components/Section/TextBlock.jsx'
import { CenterBlock } from '../../Components/CentralBlockSimple/CentralBlockSimple.jsx'
import Navbar from '../../Components/NavBar'
import { IphoneGraphicBlock } from '../../Components/IphoneGraphicBlock/IphoneGraphicBlock.jsx'

const ArivalMobile = () => {
  return (
    <main>
      <Section
        centerBlock={[
          <CenterBlock
            textWidth="754px"
            rightGraphicBlock="iphone"
            children={[
              <TextBlock textBlockType="h2" text="Overview" />,
              <TextBlock
                textBlockType="p"
                text="Opportunity: One of the top needs for both existing and prospective Arival clients was to have a mobile application to be able to access their finances on the go."
              />,
              <TextBlock
                textBlockType="p"
                text="My role: Product design, UX research, design leadership."
              />,
              <TextBlock
                textBlockType="p"
                text="Project goals: Create mobile application and design system for iOS and Android"
              />,
            ]}
          />,
        ]}
      />
      <Section
        centerBlock={[
          <CenterBlock
            textWidth="754px"
            rightGraphicBlock="iphone"
            children={[
              <TextBlock textBlockType="h2" text="Process" />,
              <TextBlock
                textBlockType="p"
                text="As I retrieved a lot of data during the Arival Web App project, I didn't need to conduct a separate stakeholder interview and primary user research (discovery calls, user interviews, etc.)."
              />,
            ]}
          />,
        ]}
      />
      <Section
        centerBlock={[
          <CenterBlock
            textWidth="754px"
            rightGraphicBlock="iphone"
            children={[
              <TextBlock textBlockType="t" text="Step 1" />,
              <TextBlock textBlockType="h3" text="Research and explorations" />,
              <TextBlock
                textBlockType="p"
                text="Research is an essential part of any project. In this case, primary research was conducted during the web app project, so there was no need to duplicate it, and I dove right into competitive and feature analysis."
              />,
              <TextBlock
                textBlockType="p"
                text="Research is an essential part of any project. In this case, primary research was conducted during the web app project, so there was no need to duplicate it, and I dove right into competitive and feature analysis."
              />,
            ]}
          />,
        ]}
      />
    </main>
  )
}

export default ArivalMobile
